Flavor Text: @{i}A true follower of Tourach took pride in achievement
             to the exclusion of other concerns.@{ui}

Flavor Text: @{i}Dedicated to the principles of Tourach, members
             of the Order of the Ebon Hand demonstrated their
             devotion with grisly rituals.@{ui}

 @{b}NO RULINGS@{ub}

@endnode
@node SOULE "Soul Exchange"

@{b}Soul Exchange@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = FE(U3)
Type    = Sorcery
Cost    = BB
Artist  = Anthony Waters

Text(FE): Sacrifice a creature, but remove it from the game instead of
          putting it in your graveyard. Take a creature from your
