@node THCHA "Thrull Champion"

@{b}Thrull Champion@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = FE(U1)
Type    = Summon Thrull (2/2)
Cost    = 4B
Artist  = Daniel Gelon

Text(FE): All Thrulls get +1/+1.
          <T>: Take control of a target Thrull.
          You lose control of target Thrull if Thrull Champion leaves
