@{b}Thrull Retainer@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = FE(U3) / 5E(U)
Type    = Enchant Creature
Cost    = B
Artist  = Ron Spencer

Text(5E): Enchanted creature gets +1/+1.
          Sacrifice Thrull Retainer: Regenerate enchanted creature.

