@{b}Thrull Wizard@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = FE(U3)
Type    = Summon Thrull (1/1)
Cost    = 2B
Artist  = Anson Maddocks

Text(FE): <1B>: Counters a target black spell if caster of target spell
          does not pay an additional <B> or 3. Play this ability as an
