@node TOUCH "Tourach's Chant"

@{b}Tourach's Chant@{ub}

Color   = Black
Rarity  = FE(U3)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = 1BB
Artist  = Richard Kane Ferguson

Text(FE): During your upkeep, pay <B> or bury Tourach's Chant. Whenever a
          player puts a forest into play, Tourach's Chant deals 3 damage to
          him or her unless that player puts a -1/-1 counter on a target
          creature he or she controls.

 @{" Rulings " link MTG_CARD_T.guide/TOURC}

